    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in stunning, showroom-quality shape\u2014you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the lot for the first time! It\u2019s been meticulously babied, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
