    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 2010 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the 3.8L flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering 385 horsepower through a sought-after 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is absolute, featuring Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for precise damping and a limited-slip differential for superior power delivery. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc aluminum fixed calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing zero fade or glazing. This vehicle presents in showroom condition with a flawless factory finish, pristine interior bolsters, and a documented service history confirming meticulous maintenance of all seals, bushings, and fluid intervals. A mechanically pure, investment-grade example for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48950.0,
